                       </span>
                     </td>
                     <td className="px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-700 text-sm">{acc.name}</td>
                     <td className="px-6 py-4">
                       <span className={`text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase ${
